title.rendered: SF Airlines (Cargo) Shenzhen, China Office Address | Email

content.rendered:
SF Airlines is a Chinese cargo airline owned by SF Express (Group) Co. The company is headquartered in the Shenzhen. It was established on 2009.

 

 

 

Verified & Updated on: 06/07/21

SF Airlines Cargo Office Contact details such as Address, Email, Fleet

Address: SF Airlines Co., Ltd., No. 1111, Hangzhan 4th Road, Bao’an International Airport, Shenzhen, Guangdong Province, 518128, P.R.China

SF Airlines Website: http://www.sf-airlines.com/sfa/en/index.html

Business contacts:

Mr. Lian Email: lianwencheng@sf-express.com

Mr.Luo Email: luoyin@sf-express.com

SF Airlines Fleet size: 65

  • Boeing 737-300SF
  • Boeing 737-400SF
  • Boeing 737-800BCF
  • Boeing 747-400ERF
  • Boeing 757-200PCF
  • Boeing 767-300ER/BCF

Is there any problem / complaint with reaching the SF Airlines, China Address or Phone number? Please report any issues using the below comment form.

Rate your experience with the SF Airlines, China: (click on the stars below)
